  "page_help": "Thandizo & FAQ",
  "help_system_title": "📋 System Description",
  "help_system_desc1": "FastWrite ndi chida chapakompiyuta chako chokudzula data kuchokera malongedwe (zinyalala, zozipemberedza, zokupemphera) pogwiritsa ntchito artificial intelligence (AI). Zimagwira ntchito m'kompiyutala chako chokha — data yako sichasankhidwa ndi munthunzu womwe, kugwiritsaninso maphunziro a platform.",
  "help_system_desc2": "Zimachitira chiyani: Mumasiza PDF yonse kapena yosiyana ndi zinyalala. Cholinga chimagwiritsa ntchito kuwu malongedwe omwe, kumakamata supplier, kumafanana ndi zowa zabwino, ndikuwula data yomwe munafotokozera (nambala ya zinyalala, tsiku, ndalama, zinthu za mizere, ndi zina). Pamapeto, mumasankhira zotsatira ku CSV kapena Excel.",
  "help_workflow_title": "🔄 Ntchito — Sitepe Sitepe",
  "help_step1_title": "Simikizani API Key",
  "help_step1_desc": "Pitani ku Settings → API Keys ndikudika API key yanu (mwachitsanzo Google Gemini). Ichi ndi chofunika — platform sichasankhire key yake. Mtengo umasilika zachangu ku account ya AI.",
  "help_step2_title": "Upload Malongedwe",
  "help_step2_desc": "Pitani ku Upload & Extract. Sumani kapena sankhani fayili ya PDF (mpaka 200 zinyalala pa fayili) ndidinge \"Register Documents\". Cholinga chimagwiritsa ntchito kuwu zinyalala ndi supplier.",
  "help_step3_title": "Pangani Zowa",
  "help_step3_desc": "Kuchokera pa Documents page, sankhani malongedwe amodzi kapena angapo ndidinge \"Labels\". Mudzapitidwa kusambanu linalake pomwe munaonetsa zinyalala kumanzere ndi mpangidwe wa zowa kumanja. Fotokozani zinthu zomwe mukufuna kuwula (mwachitsanzo nambala ya zinyalala, tsiku, ndalama, VAT) ndi zinthu za mizere. Kapenanso, pangani zowa kuchokera pa Labels page → + New Label.",
  "help_step4_title": "Kuwula Data (Batch)",
  "help_step4_desc": "Kuchokera pa Documents page, sankhani malongedwe ndidinge \"Batch\". Cholinga chimagwiritsa ntchito AI kuwula data molingana ndi zowa zililonse. Zotsatira zidavela mu documents table.",
  "help_step5_title": "Ganizirani & Lamulirani",
  "help_step5_desc": "Kuchokera pa Documents page, sankhani malongedwe ndidinge \"Approve\". Munaonetsa zinyalala kumanzere ndi kuwula data kumanja. Lozeani zabwino ndidinge \"Approve Invoice\". Kusankha kwa highlight kudalira malo oyenera m'malongedwe pamene mumaloweza mu mizere.",
  "help_step6_title": "Sankhire Mafayili",
  "help_step6_desc": "Zinyalala zalamulidwa, budzani ku Documents page. Sankhani zonyalala zalamulidwa ndidinge \"CSV\", \"XLSX\" kapena \"Line Items XLSX\" kusankhira. Ngati saankhire chilichonse, zinyalala zonse zalamulidwa zisankhidwa.",
  "help_tip_title": "💡 Chipangizo",
  "help_tip_text": "Dongosolo lalungile ndi: Upload → Labels → Batch → Approve → Export. Kumapangira pangani zowa pa mitundu yonse ya zinyalala (mwachitsanzo DEI, COSMOTE, VODAFONE) kenaka yambitsani kuwula kuchuluka. Mukapangira zowa, cholinga chimapezana kuzinyalala zatsopano kuchokera kwa supplier yomwe.",
